errorMessages.description:
The method will return a List of SessionScheduleResponse records, the first of which will contain a response in this format:
[{
  "upsertedCount": 1,
  "failedCount": 2,
  "errorMessages": [
    "Session Slot 2: Field Session_Location__c cannot be null; ",
    "Session Slot 3: Invalid date format for field Date__c; "
  ],
  "upsertedIds": [
    "a0C1c0000012345"
  ]
}]
